"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"> *本文为 Stablecoin DeFi策略系列第 1 篇，系列其它策略如下：*\\n>\\n> * *[$UST-$Mirror策略（Terra链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/b6PnhUTzoHF4_sywNXtC8OfZoZYM1gGDj22e7tpHplU)*\\n> * *xxxxxx*\\n\\n### 一、准备$UST到 MM 钱包（ETH链）\\n\\n$UST 跨链策略如下：\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/U5HcyR431ID0WwFItQa5k698jAzy3VBDtD-2ks-xYKM](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/U5HcyR431ID0WwFItQa5k698jAzy3VBDtD-2ks-xYKM)\\n\\n### 二、导入 $MIM 到钱包\\n\\n1. 进入[Abracadabra](https://abracadabra.money/)，关联MM钱包，选ETH链；\\n2. 点击右上角M样式图标；\\n3. 弹出钱包确认页面，点击「Add Token」确认；\\n\\n![导入 $MIM 代币](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/UdQU4JhM6WIyTFCshEZqF.png?height=140&width=646)\\n\\n### 三、选择UST Degenbox策略\\n\\n1. 点击页面上方「BORROW」进入；\\n2. 选择下方 $UST（右侧有明显 DegenBox标识），进入[Pool](https://abracadabra.money/pool/26)页面；\\n\\n![$UST DegenBox](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_w3S132p7fPI1coQiGaFU.png?height=258&width=1956)\\n\\n### 四、存入$UST到Abracadabra\\n\\n1. 进入「BORROW」子页面；\\n2. Liquidation price选90%，勾选Change leverage；\\n3. 关键指标：Expected Apy-112.0744%，Expected leverage-6.51x，Expected liquidation price-0.9523；\\n4. 确认交易；\\n\\n> *作者参考：Expected Apy-76.4935%，Expected leverage-4.10x，Expected liquidation price-0.8773；*\\n\\n### 五、结束\\n\\n> *本文为 Stablecoin DeFi策略系列第 1 篇，系列其它策略如下：*\\n>\\n> * *[$UST-$Mirror策略（Terra链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/b6PnhUTzoHF4_sywNXtC8OfZoZYM1gGDj22e7tpHplU)*\\n> * *xxxxxx*\",\"timestamp\":1640492694,\"title\":\"$UST-$MIM策略（ETH链）\"},\"digest\":\"WvJkuKCa5XCpT-CkHd7y8nREkLDYjtP-0Ur6XLBoABk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x2caAfafBc21f65697824f83aEAe6A9b1CB2a5B9D\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"B62I_7gRB_YYMHuuP71EhaLPoihtt7FEPmCK423yDrQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"0t-xwXug1ichLCdz7RoY0KTPuo1yNzAvgyj8b4U8Dec\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ALnKWrBC5EF4bb5h1Vo-9vMWBnSOKumvkX8tWPUx5EZx6zADHiMvGUcJAGWB2z2RoJqe57_rOPHmr_j10m6p7Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xdd0d173308dc46a16482139